## Key Architecture Decisions

- **Two-loop agent loop**: Inner loop handles tool calls + steering. Outer loop handles follow-up messages.
- **Tree-based sessions**: Conversations stored as tree (not linear), enabling branching.
- **Built-in compaction**: Old messages auto-summarized when context window overflows.
- **Queue-based steering**: Users inject messages mid-run via steer/follow-up/next-turn queues.
- **Provider abstraction**: Same API for 20+ providers. Fallback chains for reliability.

